These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, spinach
1. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Food   | asparagus | spinach |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, family
1. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | family |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, r&b
1. the fan of house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | house |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-4::.
